# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# pbrt-v4 Projects — .gitignore
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Rendered outputs and archives ---
Archive/
**/*.png
**/*.exr

# --- Generated scene files (produced by build_scene.py at runtime) ---
**/scene_files/scene.pbrt
**/scene_files/volumes/
**/scene_files/meshes/*.ply

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# --- Editor ---
.vscode/settings.json
*.swp
*.swo

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Logs ---
render_log.txt
**/scene_files/foliage.pbrt

**/scene_files/tree.pbrt
